verbose_text: Similarly, when treated with rapamycin, the ratio of LC3-II / LC3-I and the expression of both Beclin1 and p-Beclin1 were all significantly upregulated, while the expression of p62, mTOR, p-mTOR, p-S6K1 and p-4EBP1 significantly down-regulated (XREF_FIG).
